01:22:07.320 --> 01:22:08.993
Of course, you do.

01:22:10.840 --> 01:22:12.991
Miss Figgis, you're a lovely woman.

01:22:13.520 --> 01:22:15.398
And your story is amazing.

01:22:15.560 --> 01:22:18.519
I'm not surprised the flock's
up threefold since you started here.

01:22:18.680 --> 01:22:20.194
More like five times.

01:22:21.360 --> 01:22:24.558
More booze has been drunk
in the last 10 years than ever before.

01:22:24.720 --> 01:22:26.996
Because people don't wanna be told
they can't do it.

01:22:27.520 --> 01:22:30.194
The same could be said of fornication.

01:22:30.680 --> 01:22:32.034
People want it,

01:22:32.200 --> 01:22:34.396
but don't want to be told
they can't have it.

01:22:34.560 --> 01:22:35.710
Well, nor should they.

01:22:36.520 --> 01:22:37.715
I'm sorry?

01:22:38.320 --> 01:22:40.391
If people want to fornicate,
I see no reason to stop them.

01:22:40.600 --> 01:22:43.274
And if they wish to lie down with animals?

01:22:43.680 --> 01:22:45.194
Do they?

01:22:45.360 --> 01:22:46.350
I'm sorry?

01:22:46.560 --> 01:22:48.279
Do people wish to lie down with animals?

01:22:48.480 --> 01:22:49.470
Some do.

01:22:49.680 --> 01:22:52.036
And their sickness will spread
if you have your way.

01:22:52.200 --> 01:22:54.999
Forgive me. I see no correlation between
alcohol and lying down with animals.

01:22:55.160 --> 01:22:57.550
There's a correlation across all sin.

01:22:57.720 --> 01:23:03.239
It is all against the wishes of God,
therefore, all equally offensive.

01:23:03.880 --> 01:23:07.590
Let me apologize.
I think we got off on the wrong foot here.

01:23:07.760 --> 01:23:11.549
I'm just here to ask you
if you would be amenable to omitting

01:23:11.720 --> 01:23:16.078
the casino issue from your sermons,
and in exchange,

01:23:16.240 --> 01:23:17.913
we're gonna bring a business here.

01:23:18.080 --> 01:23:19.560
Business will create jobs,

01:23:19.760 --> 01:23:24.596
which will reduce the sinfulness
that comes with poverty and idle hands.

01:23:25.240 --> 01:23:27.197
We'd be willing
to contribute to the church.

01:23:27.360 --> 01:23:29.955
Hell, we'd be willing to
build a few churches.

01:23:36.440 --> 01:23:40.150
If God rewrites the Bible
to cast gambling as virtuous,

01:23:40.320 --> 01:23:43.119
I will refrain from speaking against it.

01:23:43.600 --> 01:23:45.592
But until then,

01:23:46.120 --> 01:23:49.591
we don't get to pick
our sins, Mr. Coughlin.

01:23:54.960 --> 01:23:56.440
I can't do it.

01:23:57.160 --> 01:23:58.150
What?

01:23:58.640 --> 01:24:01.155
She's gonna fuck up the whole deal.
What do you mean you can't do it?

01:24:01.320 --> 01:24:04.040
I know. No one touches her.

01:24:06.240 --> 01:24:07.879
That's a mistake.

01:24:09.320 --> 01:24:10.800
No shit.

01:24:24.640 --> 01:24:26.279
MAN: Can we get you anything?

01:24:26.440 --> 01:24:28.318
Oh, we're okay. Thanks.

01:24:28.920 --> 01:24:32.630
We know you men are busy,
and we don't want to waste your time.

01:24:32.800 --> 01:24:36.157
We're not going to invest
in the casino at the Ritz.

01:24:39.320 --> 01:24:41.516
(STUTTERS) Are you sure about that?

01:24:41.720 --> 01:24:44.679
I'm afraid so. The publicity is too much.

01:24:44.840 --> 01:24:46.991
One woman preaching in a fucking tent?

01:24:47.160 --> 01:24:51.677
Yes, because the casino would represent
only 2% of our total holdings.

01:24:51.840 --> 01:24:57.120
And we can't appear to be
a company of Irish and Italian Catholics

01:24:57.320 --> 01:25:00.313
turning white Protestant girls
into drug addicts.

01:25:01.200 --> 01:25:04.352
The people I work for
are gonna be very upset about this.

01:25:04.520 --> 01:25:06.989
We aren't men to be muscled or conned.

01:25:07.200 --> 01:25:10.557
We're an institution.
We can't be bribed or bullied

01:25:10.720 --> 01:25:13.076
because I simply represent
the vested interest

01:25:13.240 --> 01:25:14.799
of a board of governors.

01:25:15.000 --> 01:25:18.038
We are the landed
white gentry in this country

01:25:18.200 --> 01:25:22.877
and we have no plans
to carve off a strip of this country,

01:25:23.040 --> 01:25:26.238
which we have gone
to great pains to break and colonize

01:25:26.400 --> 01:25:31.555
and hand it over to Catholics,
Jews, darkies or dagos.

01:25:33.000 --> 01:25:35.834
It's just a bigger, better racket.
That's all.

01:25:36.000 --> 01:25:39.072
Keeping the money in your hands
and out of the hands of people like us.

01:25:42.560 --> 01:25:44.392
All those people,

01:25:44.760 --> 01:25:46.240
the Negro

01:25:46.400 --> 01:25:50.394
on whose back you went
to great pains to break this country

01:25:50.560 --> 01:25:53.075
and the immigrants
who came over here with nothing

01:25:53.240 --> 01:25:54.993
and worked their fingers
to the fucking bone,

01:25:55.240 --> 01:25:59.234
all believed it
when you told them they could get ahead.

01:25:59.520 --> 01:26:03.196
And one day, and I may not live to see it,
they're gonna figure it out.

01:26:03.360 --> 01:26:06.353
But I tell you what.
I'd hate to fucking be you.

01:26:06.520 --> 01:26:10.912
Standing between those people
and what they deserve.

01:26:13.400 --> 01:26:15.790
Good luck to you. (SOFTLY) Prick.

01:26:19.440 --> 01:26:21.636
Would have been a hell of a casino.

01:26:22.040 --> 01:26:23.918
You'll get another chance.

01:26:24.600 --> 01:26:26.592
Things swing back around.

01:26:27.080 --> 01:26:28.912
Not all things.

01:26:29.600 --> 01:26:32.479
JOE: They announced it on the radio
just when we got back.

01:26:34.960 --> 01:26:38.397
President-elect Roosevelt
promised to sign the Cullen-Harrison Act

01:26:38.560 --> 01:26:43.191
the minute he was elected,
effectively ending Prohibition.

01:26:46.720 --> 01:26:48.757
(PHONE RINGING)

01:26:57.960 --> 01:27:00.111
(CONTINUES RINGING)

01:27:21.160 --> 01:27:23.516
- Hello, Miss Figgis.
- LORETTA: Mr. Coughlin.

01:27:23.680 --> 01:27:24.670
- May I?
- Yes.

01:27:24.880 --> 01:27:27.236
- Just for a minute?
- Yeah. Please sit.

01:27:28.960 --> 01:27:30.872
You're looking very well.

01:27:32.200 --> 01:27:34.795
I see you're not wearing white.

01:27:35.640 --> 01:27:37.711
It's almost white. (CHUCKLES)

01:27:37.880 --> 01:27:38.870
Would you like a menu?

01:27:39.040 --> 01:27:40.838
Thank you very much.
Could I have a cup of coffee, please?

01:27:41.000 --> 01:27:41.990
Sure.

01:27:45.000 --> 01:27:45.990
Thank you.

01:27:53.000 --> 01:27:55.799
Why does my father hate you so much?

01:27:56.840 --> 01:27:58.320
(SIGHS)

01:27:58.840 --> 01:28:03.039
I'm a crook. He's the chief of police.
That's how it goes, I guess.

01:28:03.520 --> 01:28:05.318
No. He liked you.

01:28:06.000 --> 01:28:07.832
He said you were the Mayor of Ybor.

01:28:08.880 --> 01:28:10.712
- (CHUCKLES) Is that what he said?
- Mmm.

01:28:14.720 --> 01:28:16.040
What did you do?

01:28:18.840 --> 01:28:20.559
To him?

01:28:24.480 --> 01:28:26.870
(EXHALES DEEPLY)

01:28:33.120 --> 01:28:35.316
We had photographs.

01:28:40.080 --> 01:28:41.753
And you showed them to him.

01:28:42.240 --> 01:28:43.720
I showed him two.

01:28:44.360 --> 01:28:46.397
How many did you have?

01:28:47.280 --> 01:28:48.873
All of them.

01:28:54.240 --> 01:28:56.357
We're all going to hell.

01:28:57.920 --> 01:29:00.037
I don't think you're going to hell.

01:29:00.200 --> 01:29:02.078
You know what I learned

01:29:02.640 --> 01:29:07.237
as I've been thrusting my soul out to God?

01:29:07.440 --> 01:29:08.590
What?

01:29:10.320 --> 01:29:12.437
This is heaven.

01:29:13.760 --> 01:29:15.160
Right here.

01:29:16.280 --> 01:29:17.600
We're in it now.

01:29:18.120 --> 01:29:19.793
Then how come it looks like hell?

01:29:20.360 --> 01:29:22.272
Because we fucked it all up.

01:29:22.480 --> 01:29:24.278
(CHUCKLES SOFTLY)

01:29:30.880 --> 01:29:33.270
After my trials,

01:29:37.280 --> 01:29:39.795
I slept in the bed of my childhood.

01:29:43.960 --> 01:29:45.997
I felt certain again.

01:29:47.640 --> 01:29:49.313
I missed that.

01:29:54.960 --> 01:29:57.316
I don't know if there is a God.

01:30:01.200 --> 01:30:03.157
But I hope there is.

01:30:06.320 --> 01:30:08.551
(VOICE BREAKING) And I hope he's kind.

01:30:11.320 --> 01:30:13.710
Wouldn't that be swell?

01:30:17.360 --> 01:30:19.033
Yes, it would be.

01:30:24.000 --> 01:30:25.354
(SIGHS)

01:30:26.000 --> 01:30:28.834
You seem not to despair.
Do you have a secret?

01:30:29.000 --> 01:30:30.832
No. No secrets.

01:30:32.360 --> 01:30:33.874
I have my wife.

01:30:35.520 --> 01:30:36.840
That's enough.

01:30:37.560 --> 01:30:40.473
But what if you lose her?

01:30:44.960 --> 01:30:46.189
What are you gonna do now?

01:30:47.280 --> 01:30:48.600
What do you mean?

01:30:49.120 --> 01:30:51.874
You stopped me. Stopped the casino.

01:30:52.040 --> 01:30:54.919
Law couldn't do it.
The people couldn't do it.

01:30:55.080 --> 01:30:57.197
The Klan couldn't do it.

01:30:57.360 --> 01:30:58.350
You did it.

01:30:58.520 --> 01:30:59.954
I didn't get rid of alcohol.

01:31:00.120 --> 01:31:02.191
No. That was too big.

01:31:02.360 --> 01:31:05.398
But you've stopped gambling, and before
you came along, that was a lock.

01:31:05.600 --> 01:31:07.353
I did do that, didn't I?

01:31:07.560 --> 01:31:08.880
- Yes, you did.
- (LAUGHS)

01:31:11.880 --> 01:31:14.031
What's your father gonna do?

01:31:15.400 --> 01:31:17.392
Sit in his chair, I guess.

01:31:18.160 --> 01:31:19.958
Blind with rage

01:31:21.320 --> 01:31:24.119
that men touched his daughter
the way he used to touch his wife.

01:31:24.280 --> 01:31:25.794
And worse.

01:31:32.000 --> 01:31:36.552
He goes around the house
whispering one word over and over.

01:31:37.080 --> 01:31:38.434
What word?

01:31:39.560 --> 01:31:40.994
Repent.

01:31:44.600 --> 01:31:47.752
Repent, repent.

01:31:50.320 --> 01:31:54.075
Give him some time.
Maybe he'll come out of it.

01:32:18.960 --> 01:32:21.236
(INDISTINCT TALKING)

01:32:28.360 --> 01:32:31.194
We heard from Boston.
All three trucks made it up there fine.

01:32:31.360 --> 01:32:33.158
Same payoffs as last week,
so it's no problem.

01:32:33.360 --> 01:32:34.476
Good. Good, good.

01:32:34.640 --> 01:32:37.951
And Loretta Figgis
cut her own throat yesterday.

01:32:39.160 --> 01:32:40.389
What?

01:32:40.760 --> 01:32:42.831
Yeah, she did it at home
in the chief's bed, they say.

01:32:44.840 --> 01:32:45.956
Gotta give it to her.

01:32:47.480 --> 01:32:49.836
She's got moxie. I couldn't do that.

01:32:51.000 --> 01:32:53.469
I don't know,
I guess some things are meant to be.

01:32:53.640 --> 01:32:56.470
Hell, she could've done it three months
earlier, and done us all a fucking favor.

01:32:59.560 --> 01:33:00.835
Too late.

01:33:14.400 --> 01:33:16.232
ESTEBAN: You blame yourself?

01:33:17.000 --> 01:33:19.913
She went out west
as so many other girls do.

01:33:20.160 --> 01:33:22.197
And she was preyed upon.

01:33:22.360 --> 01:33:23.510
Not by you.

01:33:23.680 --> 01:33:25.353
By men like me.

01:33:25.520 --> 01:33:28.240
Men who get the booze,
they get the girls...

01:33:28.400 --> 01:33:30.073
They get the drugs.

01:33:30.240 --> 01:33:31.879
One hand washes the other.

01:33:33.240 --> 01:33:34.754
(SPEAKS SPANISH)

01:33:36.040 --> 01:33:38.032
We are not our brother's keeper.

01:33:38.200 --> 01:33:41.079
In fact, it is an insult to our brother
to believe we are.

01:33:41.520 --> 01:33:43.000
Look at these people.

01:33:44.200 --> 01:33:47.910
If this man, say, dies of drunkenness

01:33:48.080 --> 01:33:50.037
is it our fault?

01:33:53.240 --> 01:33:55.630
When did you take this picture?

01:33:56.440 --> 01:33:57.920
A month ago.

01:33:58.920 --> 01:34:00.400
Are you sure?

01:34:02.400 --> 01:34:06.440
I took this picture myself
a month and three days ago.

01:34:06.600 --> 01:34:07.716
Why?

01:34:09.080 --> 01:34:11.436
Because that woman died in 1927.

01:34:20.040 --> 01:34:21.315
(WAVES CRASHING)

01:34:54.320 --> 01:34:57.438
There has never been
anyone like you in my life.

01:34:59.440 --> 01:35:02.433
And one day,
I'm gonna be good enough for you.

01:35:04.320 --> 01:35:06.880
- DION: Are you sure it's her?
- You tell me.

01:35:08.120 --> 01:35:10.476
- You tell Graciela?
- Of course I told her.

01:35:11.960 --> 01:35:13.280
Jesus Christ.

01:35:14.280 --> 01:35:15.794
What? You wouldn't tell your woman?

01:35:16.000 --> 01:35:16.990
No.

01:35:17.160 --> 01:35:19.755
No, I don't tell them shit.
But you're more of a nance than me.

01:35:19.920 --> 01:35:21.070
What'd you say?

01:35:21.240 --> 01:35:23.960
"Look, sorry, hon, that girl
I was bent out of shape over for years,

01:35:24.120 --> 01:35:25.918
"she's not dead. She's in Miami.

01:35:26.080 --> 01:35:28.959
"Don't make
a big fucking thing out of it."

01:35:35.800 --> 01:35:37.154
When you going?

01:35:37.520 --> 01:35:39.034
- Going where?
- What do you mean, where?

01:35:39.200 --> 01:35:41.476
You found out this girl
you used to be bugs for is 200 miles away.

01:35:41.640 --> 01:35:43.120
When you going?

01:35:48.280 --> 01:35:51.034
- Probably go after this thing with Maso.
- Good.

01:35:51.200 --> 01:35:53.351
Give you something to live for.

01:35:53.560 --> 01:35:55.040
What does that mean?

01:35:55.200 --> 01:35:58.511
Him and his guys are
taking over half a train to get down here.

01:35:59.840 --> 01:36:01.559
That's a big fucking entourage.

01:36:02.600 --> 01:36:05.035
Ah, bullshit. I ain't worried about it.

01:36:05.200 --> 01:36:07.032
There's no percentage in killing us.

01:36:07.760 --> 01:36:10.514
We do 11 and a half million dollars a year
from rum alone

01:36:10.680 --> 01:36:12.592
in this fucking cow town.

01:36:13.040 --> 01:36:14.440
What's he want to kill us for?

01:36:14.600 --> 01:36:17.672
All we do is send him bags of money
up to his mansion in fucking Nahant.

01:36:17.840 --> 01:36:19.035
I don't like the signs.

01:36:19.200 --> 01:36:20.919
- What fucking signs?
- We lost the casino.

01:36:21.080 --> 01:36:22.070
We never moved on narcotics,

01:36:22.240 --> 01:36:24.960
and you're Irish in a world where there
ain't much of a shortage in guineas.

01:36:25.120 --> 01:36:28.716
Okay? You're walking into a building
where he bought up every room.

01:36:28.880 --> 01:36:30.394
I can't hide a weapon. Nothing.

01:36:30.560 --> 01:36:32.631
You're going in blind
and we'll be outside.

01:36:35.360 --> 01:36:37.192
Is that enough signs for you?

01:36:38.640 --> 01:36:40.552
(SIGHS DEEPLY)

01:36:42.520 --> 01:36:44.193
JOE: I need you to do something for me.

01:36:45.160 --> 01:36:48.437
I need you to go stay in Miami
for just a little while.

01:36:51.600 --> 01:36:53.193
How long is a little while?

01:36:53.560 --> 01:36:55.392
I don't know. Not too long.

01:36:56.400 --> 01:36:59.279
I'm not gonna have your address.
I want you to give it to Dion.

01:36:59.440 --> 01:37:01.432
When the time comes,
he'll tell me where you are

01:37:01.600 --> 01:37:03.592
and I'll come get you.

01:37:05.920 --> 01:37:10.073
So, you can find out if
you are as cruel as you need to be?

01:37:10.600 --> 01:37:12.034
I guess so.

01:37:13.800 --> 01:37:15.029
Joseph.

01:37:16.600 --> 01:37:21.231
Even if you win today's battle,
there's so much violence in what you do.

01:37:28.400 --> 01:37:29.470
(SIGHS)

01:37:29.760 --> 01:37:30.910
Come here.

01:38:34.960 --> 01:38:36.440
Gino, where you living now?

01:38:36.600 --> 01:38:37.716
Neponset.

01:38:37.880 --> 01:38:39.473
Oh. Settling down?

01:38:39.680 --> 01:38:43.117
Two kids. A mugliera, 'a casa.
Whole thing.

01:38:43.280 --> 01:38:46.239
- You got any?
- None for me.

01:38:46.520 --> 01:38:48.716
There's never a right time.

01:38:50.320 --> 01:38:52.073
(ELEVATOR DINGS)

01:39:12.320 --> 01:39:13.549
This way.

01:39:27.120 --> 01:39:28.554
(KNOCKS ON DOOR)

01:39:30.360 --> 01:39:31.714
How are you, my son?

01:39:33.040 --> 01:39:34.030
Fine.

01:39:34.880 --> 01:39:36.553
Fausto, see if Dion needs anything.

01:39:51.440 --> 01:39:53.238
So, how've you been?

01:39:53.400 --> 01:39:54.914
Good. You?

01:39:55.080 --> 01:39:57.231
More good days than bad.

01:39:57.400 --> 01:39:58.390
Good.

01:40:02.920 --> 01:40:05.719
This is the filly
who fucked up the whole casino thing?

01:40:07.240 --> 01:40:09.038
Yeah, that's her.

01:40:09.200 --> 01:40:11.590
Why didn't you clip her then?

01:40:12.280 --> 01:40:13.600
Too much blowback.

01:40:13.760 --> 01:40:15.080
That's not it.

01:40:16.400 --> 01:40:18.392
You're not a killer, Joseph.

01:40:18.560 --> 01:40:20.472
You are a bandit in a suit.

01:40:20.640 --> 01:40:24.111
That's why you didn't kill that
puttana pazza.

01:40:24.280 --> 01:40:26.636
You know how much money
this place was doing when I got here?

01:40:26.800 --> 01:40:28.792
- You know what it's doing now?
- But that's all rum.

01:40:29.000 --> 01:40:31.390
You neglected the girls and the narcotics.

01:40:31.560 --> 01:40:33.279
I went after the rum
'cause it was the most profitable,

01:40:33.440 --> 01:40:35.159
and I added four houses in my time here.

01:40:35.320 --> 01:40:36.913
Yeah, but you could have added more.

01:40:37.080 --> 01:40:38.150
Maso, look...

01:40:38.320 --> 01:40:39.913
Mr. Pescatore!

01:40:42.800 --> 01:40:46.760
I ran Ybor. I ran Tampa.
Did you ever have a problem?

01:40:46.920 --> 01:40:47.990
You did more than that.

01:40:48.160 --> 01:40:50.231
You ran the whole coast.

01:40:50.440 --> 01:40:54.639
You boxed out Albert.
Put him in a little piss corner of Miami.

01:40:54.960 --> 01:40:56.758
I've been through the books.

01:40:57.320 --> 01:40:58.959
You made us a force down here.

01:40:59.360 --> 01:41:02.592
But now what?
"No Irish need apply?" What can I be?

01:41:02.760 --> 01:41:03.796
What I fucking tell you to be.

01:41:04.480 --> 01:41:07.279
Before you get a fucking pop
in the mouth, Mick.

01:41:09.640 --> 01:41:11.996
You can be consigliere.

01:41:12.680 --> 01:41:16.037
You teach Digger the ropes. Meet people.

01:41:16.600 --> 01:41:18.637
Teach him to fish.

01:41:18.840 --> 01:41:20.638
But you need to take a haircut.

01:41:21.320 --> 01:41:22.720
What kind of a haircut?

01:41:23.520 --> 01:41:24.954
Digger gets your take.

01:41:26.520 --> 01:41:28.159
(SIGHS)

01:41:29.120 --> 01:41:31.680
Look, Mr. Pescatore,

01:41:32.560 --> 01:41:34.517
I think it's a fabulous idea.

01:41:34.880 --> 01:41:37.190
